{"tid":1457962,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"經過今日 我覺得我地輸硬","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T13:10:14.000Z","uid":27558,"like":13,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a867684ba970f4aceaf15ea3fb71607774d938e4","tid":1457962,"uid":27558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:39:42.000Z","msg":"原本今日我地好成功癱瘓機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後慢慢岀現假消息<br />\nCut network/無旅客/無機鐵/機場熄燈 武警清場等等<br />\n跟住啲人就信晒 開始驚 跟住走撚晒<br />\n我大叫啲人唔好走 呢個機會好難得 咁多人係機場 仲要癱瘓<br />\n最後比人指住我話我係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜嘢不割蓆 不分化 全部都係假嘅 <br />\n明明和理非機場全世界都知<br />\n但啲人諗都唔諗 即刻走 叫人唔走果啲即係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算佢真係放tg清場 都係攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最戇鳩係有人話目標已達成<br />\n點達成？癱瘓機場？唔好戇鳩啦<br />\n癱瘓機場只係我地籌碼 五大訴求先係我地目標呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再係咁嘅心態落去 只會輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日原本見到希望 但最後得到嘅係失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0692976efee22891e7fdf483be60dd40ee09494","tid":1457962,"uid":27558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86ae2608dc6f1b6e3abc28247a4506b2fce128d","tid":1457962,"uid":144996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:41:18.000Z","msg":"幫推 聽日照入"},{"pid":"67a978c5c2377c4a4174dc902cdd61f593292c22","tid":1457962,"uid":21873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:41:27.000Z","msg":"聽日會復航嫁咩<br />\n唔會短期戰成功<br />\n聽日再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最緊要唔好灰心"},{"pid":"5fcaab006bd3232ad4a37c53f07e5fb254cb74e9","tid":1457962,"uid":27558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67a978c5c2377c4a4